If you're an old school fellow trapped in a modern world, you can bring back some of ‘your’ era’s style and make a fashion statement with this item. It’s a constructed blazer with multiple retro colors and patterns, made of a high-quality cotton blend.

Name: Dandy Fan
Description: Embracing your inner patriot and still looking your best: that’s what Dandy Fan is about. This red, white and blue blazer has a stylish cotton tape trim, a game day food lining and is made of a comfortable and delicate double-knit jersey. It lets you win the ‘best-dressed supporter trophy’ at any sports event.

Name: Park Ranger
Description: Inspired by the look of park rangers, this blazer is a modernized and classy version of an iconic ranger jacket. It’s a soft, sleek blazer with shoulder epaulettes, functional pockets, wooden buttons and merit badges for that ultimate outdoor look. Despite its forest green camouflage color, it will not fail to make you stand out.

Name: Constellations
Description: This blazer is inspired by and a reflection of the beauty of our galaxy. It’s a smooth velvet jacket with an all-over black foil print, depicting the Milky Way’s most famous constellations. The galaxy lining perfectly complements the constellations pattern. Yes: it’s written in the stars that this jacket makes you look out of this world.
